### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### SSE events (open in browser or curl)
# curl -N http://localhost:8080/events?sid=test-user-123

### List subscriptions (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{azure_token}}

### Chat - Ask about resources
POST http://localhost:8080/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{azure_token}}

{
    "message": "What resources do I have in my subscription?",
    "subscription_id": "{{subscription_id}}"
}

### Chat - Cost analysis
POST http://localhost:8080/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{azure_token}}

{
    "message": "Show me a cost breakdown by resource group for the last 30 days and generate a visual report",
    "subscription_id": "{{subscription_id}}"
}

### Chat - Find unused resources
POST http://localhost:8080/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{azure_token}}

{
    "message": "Find all orphaned and unused resources in my subscription and generate a report",
    "subscription_id": "{{subscription_id}}"
}

### Chat - Resource health
POST http://localhost:8080/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{azure_token}}

{
    "message": "Check the health status of all my resources",
    "subscription_id": "{{subscription_id}}"
}

### Chat - Dashboard
POST http://localhost:8080/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{azure_token}}

{
    "message": "Generate a comprehensive dashboard of my Azure environment showing resources, costs, and health",
    "subscription_id": "{{subscription_id}}"
}

### Clear chat history
POST http://localhost:8080/chat/clear
Authorization: Bearer {{azure_token}}
